# About Shrtn

**Shrtn** is an open-source, self-hosted URL shortener designed for maximum privacy, performance, and ease of use. Built with a focus on simplicity and extensibility, Shrtn empowers you to run your own link management solution‚Äîfree from third-party restrictions and data harvesting.

